{"tid":2269601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耀才許繹彬：螞蟻H股一旦擱置上市  孖展息或無法退回","createTime":"2020-11-03T14:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T15:24:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0659e58022c216853c69d09877a23e785f9bdb0b","tid":2269601,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:12:11.000Z","msg":"螞蟻集團（6688）突然公布A股暫緩上市，耀才集團執行董事兼行政總裁許繹彬表示，螞蟻集團現階段只宣布暫緩A股上市計劃，H股是否亦跟隨暫緩，要視乎其公司及包銷的取態；他指出，一旦證實螞蟻H股擱置，稍後會展開退還本金的安排，至於散戶的孖展利息開支則可能無法退回。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1604410476042&amp;issue=20201103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1604410476042%26issue%3D20201103&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=4b6eba79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1604410476042&amp;issue=20201103</a>"},{"pid":"ad29341f801d854d81bab68bb8652935589ec6fe","tid":2269601,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"至於散戶的孖展利息開支，應該有可能會<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">繼續支付</span></span>有關的孖展利息，無法退回"},{"pid":"9f2d129c3cc6ef567c5549481d10d26fb33e6f24","tid":2269601,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6aa331562180c8f601f687f67e79e9a6e0e8d89","tid":2269601,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"IFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gi